      "text": "情報番組のレポーターだ\nロケをして最新イベントやグルメ情報を伝える仕事だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a job as a reporter for an informational program. You'll be doing\nlocation shoots and reporting the latest events and gourmet information.",
